      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，PaymentGateway作为入口节点。AuthVault是认证存储，TransactionQueue是交易队列。这两个是并行关系还是先后关系？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "B",
        "D"
